      <body>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><dateline rend="right"><pb facs="MS-SCHNITZLER-B-00096-B-000-00037"/><date>25. 9. 07</date></dateline><salute>lieber Gu<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tav,</salute></opener><p>hier 2 Sitze für <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L04035-1"/><rs type="event" ref="#pmb186202"><date>Freitag</date></rs><note type="commentary" corresp="K_L04035-1">Die <rs type="event" ref="#pmb186202">Premiere von <rs type="person" ref="#pmb2121">Schnitzlers</rs><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><rs type="work" ref="#pmb29823">Das Märchen</rs></rs> fand am <date when="1907-09-27">27. 9. 1907</date> im <rs type="place" ref="#pmb60854">Wiener Bürgertheater</rs> statt. <rs type="person" ref="#pmb12740">Schwarzkopf</rs> nahm teil.</note> –</p><p>aber Sie mü<c rendition="#langesS">s</c><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>en nicht!!</p><closer>Wir grüßen Sie beide herzlich<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t<lb/> Ihr<lb/><signed>Arthur</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
